{
  "chapter": 66,
  "chapter_summary": "铜先生震怒之下以掌力毁树发泄，却答应花无缺等三个月再杀小鱼儿，并承诺保护其不受伤害。小鱼儿趁机试探，发现铜先生与移花宫主间隐藏着秘密——他们执意要花无缺亲手杀人，其中必有蹊跷。小鱼儿巧妙利用保护期大胆挑衅，请花无缺代传口信给燕南天。花无缺与小鱼儿互认朋友，虽知只有三个月情谊，仍珍惜这份意外之交。次日花无缺摆脱江别鹤监视，赴花林与铁心兰重逢，两人在落花中倾诉心事，铁心兰满怀愧疚，花无缺温柔以对。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你定要等到三个月后才肯杀他，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你既重信义，我身为前辈，怎能令你为难，你要等三个月，我就让你等三个月又有何妨？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "现在，你走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那么他……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "先生难道要……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "无论他会不会失信，这三个月里，我都要好好的保护他，不使他受到丝毫伤损，三个月后，再将他完完整整地交给你……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "要你如此费心保护我，怎么好意思呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "保护你这么样一个人，还用得着我费心么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你以为我很容易保护，你可错了，我这人别的毛病没有，就喜欢找人麻烦。江湖中要杀我的人，可不止一个。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "除了花无缺外，谁也杀不了你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你话已说得这么满，在这三个月里，我若受了损伤，可真不知道你有什么面目来见人了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在这三个月里，你若有丝毫损伤，惟我是问。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那我就放心了。在这三个月里，我无论做什么，都没关系了，反正任何人都伤不了我。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你只管放心，在这三个月里，你无论做什么事，都做不出的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那倒未必……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你还不走？等在这里做什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你放心走吧，三个月后，我会在那地方等你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但现在我想和他悄悄说句话，你放不放心？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "天下根本没有一件可令我不放心的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你本事虽不算小，但牛也未必吹得太大了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你敢无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我为何不敢，在这三个月里，反正没有人能伤到我的，是么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "只可惜他戴个鬼脸，否则他现在的脸色一定好看得很。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你要说什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "明天下午，燕南天燕大侠在今天那花林等我，你能不能代我去告诉他，我不能赴约了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "燕南天？……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我知道你跟他有些过不去，所以你纵不答应我，我也不会怪你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这三个月，你我是朋友，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你很好，我交你这朋友，总算不冤枉。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "可惜只有三个月。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "天下有很多出人意料的事，这些事每天都有几件发生，说不定我过两天就能看见你也未可知。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我总不相信奇迹。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我若不相信奇迹，你想我现在还能笑得出么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "奇迹是不会出现的。花无缺，你还不走么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人若是非死不可，能死在他手上，总比死在别人手上好得多了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我为何要恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他的尊长，杀死了你的父母。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我父母死的时候，他只怕还未出生哩！他师父做的事，与他又有何关系？他师父吃了饭，难道还能要他代替屙屎么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我问你，你为何要我恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你恨不恨他，与我又有何关系？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "是呀，我恨不恨他，和你没关系，你又何苦如此关心？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他要亲手杀死我，而又说不出原因来，我本已觉得有些奇怪，现在更是越来越奇怪了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你虽不恨他，他却恨你，所以要杀你，这有什么好奇怪的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你以为他真的恨我么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他非恨你不可！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这就是我所奇怪的。你和他师父，要杀我都很容易，但你们却都不动手，所以我觉得你们其实也并不是真的要我死，只不过是要他动手杀我而已，你们好像一定要看他亲手杀我，才觉得开心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "要他杀你，就是要你死，这又有何分别？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这是有分别的，而且这分别还微妙得很，我知道这其中必定有个很奇怪的原因，只可惜我现在还猜不出而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这秘密普天之下，只有两个人知道，而他们绝不会告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "移花宫主自然是知道的……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "自然。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "text": "移花宫主便是姐妹两人，你既然说这秘密天下只有两个人知道，那么你又怎会知道的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tong_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "铜先生",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你说的话太多了，现在闭起嘴吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "愚兄昨夜与人有约，不得已只好出去走了走，回来时才知道贤弟你独自喝了不少闷酒，竟喝醉了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "现在不知是什么时辰了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "已过了午时。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "呀，我这一觉睡得竟这么迟……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "愚兄陪贤弟出去逛逛如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "小弟已在城里住了如此久，江兄还担心小弟会迷路么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "既是如此，愚兄就到前面去瞧瞧段姑娘了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "遵命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺呀花无缺，我虽然一心想结纳于你，但你若想对不起我，就莫怪我也要对不起你了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喝茶……他一个人会到茶馆里去喝么？难道他约了什么人在那茶馆里见面不成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "花公子在那茶馆里坐了很久，并没有人过去和他说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "花公子此刻在街头瞧王铁臂练把式。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_da_han",
      "text": "那种骗人的把式，他也能看得下去？……你们可瞧见那边人丛里，有什么人和他说话么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_da_han",
      "text": "现在谁在盯着他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "大汉",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "那条街是宋三和李阿牛管的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "花公子忽然不见了！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_song_san",
      "text": "你难道是瞎子么？光天化日之下，行人往来不断的街道上，他绝不能施展轻功，又怎会突然不见？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "那王铁臂和徒弟练完单刀破花枪，就轮到他女儿耍流星锤，谁知她正使到一招“云里捉月”，流星锤的链子忽然断了，小西瓜般大小的流星锤，冲天飞了出去，瞧把式的人都怕它掉下来打着脑袋，惊呼着四下飞逃，那把式场立刻就乱了。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_song_san",
      "text": "流星锤的链子，是怎么断的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "小的不知道。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_song_san",
      "text": "你只怕是瞧王铁臂的女儿瞧晕了头吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_san",
      "speaker_name": "宋三",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "小……小的不敢。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_song_san",
      "text": "你这双眼睛既然如此不中用，还留着它干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花无缺哪里去了？他为何要躲着我？莫非他真的和江小鱼有约，要来对付我？这两人若是联成一路，我该如何是好？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "宁可我负天下人，莫令一人负我……江别鹤呀江别鹤，这句话你千万忘记不得！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花开花落，顷刻化泥，人生又何尝不是如此？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你好么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你想不到来的是我，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "瞧见你没有受伤，我实在很高兴。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我本来有许多话想对你说，却不知该怎么说才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "有些人是很难被忘记的，有时你纵然以为自己忘却了他，但只要一见他，他的一言一笑，就都又重回到你心头……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你……你能原谅我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你根本没有什么事要求人原谅的。我若是你，说不定也会如此。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但我实在对不起你，你…你为什么不骂我？不怪我？那样我心里反而会好受些，你的同情和了解，只有令我更痛苦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 66,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    }
  ],
